HEADWORD: Equipensate
<hw>E`qui*pen"sate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Equi-</ets> + <ets>pensatus</ets>, p. p. of pensare to weigh.
Cf. <er>Equipoise</er>.]</ety> <def>To weigh equally; to esteem
alike.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
